  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0bae\u0ba9\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The decision regarding the petition against Ranil today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Will the petition filed challenging the fact that United National Party leader Ranil Wickremesinghe was brought to Parliament through the national list be investigated? Isn't it? The High Court will announce tomorrow.",
        "The petition has been filed by the general secretary of Vinivita Peramuna, lawyer Nagananda Kodithuvaku.",
        "Pointing out that this petition was filed out of time, the Attorney General's Department also pointed out in the court that such a petition was filed and dismissed.",
        "Also, the President's lawyer who appeared in the court on behalf of Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe said that this petition should be dismissed.",
        "In this situation, will the petition be heard? Isn't it? A three-judge bench of the High Court will announce today. (a)"
      ],
